{"tid":2234750,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓仔突然食量減少，點解會咁？","createTime":"2020-10-08T06:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T04:56:27.000Z","uid":231905,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"152857229dccbf9fea3f1e610a68386ec99f962a","tid":2234750,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:21:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ua5aBNU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fua5aBNU.png&h=19839873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n已經book左vet睇，想問下巴絲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 四個月大美短<br />\n上星期五打第一針，打完少攰，於是冇同佢玩(以前一日兩次playtime，每次5分鐘)<br />\n之後佢就開始越食越少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到今日食少左40%<br />\n行為上冇咩分別，但稍為訓多左郁少左。但老實講唔識分係大個仔懶d定有問題<br />\n朝早起身d糧都冇點郁過，固定早晚食罐都好似冇胃口要聞同舔兩次，第三次先食一半(以前極速清哂)<br />\n<br />\n自己諗有幾個可能性:<br />\n1. 打針副作用。但都幾乎成個星期<br />\n2. 轉季唔食野。但呢個唔識confirm，同埋冇理由少40%咁多<br />\n3. 冇playtime食少左？第一次養貓真係唔知玩同唔玩差幾遠，求意見<br />\n4. 誤食左野？ 佢行為其實都好正常<br />\n<br />\n集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b79c97cb32953e23d04670cfe2bb311425476212","tid":2234750,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:23:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係當大家獸醫，純粹問下經驗同brainstorm下"},{"pid":"629f7509fa422562040ab9f0c86ea14f9bec4756","tid":2234750,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:23:36.000Z","msg":"btw 應該唔係食厭？<br />\n罐頭有兩隻味都係一樣食咁少<br />\n連乾糧都少食左"},{"pid":"7f32d67de36cf83466c76b6099094090c9531a69","tid":2234750,"uid":114062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:24:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sli